-- Seed all 104 FIFA World Cup 2026 matches.
-- Group stage matches (1-72) have real team names.
-- Knockout matches (73-104) use placeholders that the admin will update
-- as the tournament progresses:
--   1A, 2A, ...     winner / runner-up of Group A (etc.)
--   3A/B/C/D/F      best-third-placed team from one of those groups
--   W73             winner of game 73
--   L101            loser of game 101 (used for bronze final)
--
-- Kickoff times are in local time with timezone offset.
-- Postgres stores them as TIMESTAMPTZ (UTC internally), so the offset
-- preserves the original local time for human readability of this file.

